default amount of cycling is part of dealing with the issue of danger towards cyclists. 
default3.5.3.default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultThis should include not just provision of attractive highway and off-road environments, but also the realisation that inappropriate behaviour towards cyclists will become les
defaults socially tolerable.
default3.5.4.default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultIt should also include:
default3.5.5.default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
defaultProgrammes to address other issues limiting take up of cycling, such as inadequate secure and convenient home cycle parking, 
default3.5.6.default&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
